                            <comment id="17108904" author="paulk" created="Sat, 16 May 2020 07:40:13 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Status: the prod code fix for this is applied in GROOVY_2_5_X, GROOVY_3_0_X and master (for Groovy 4). The test currently relies on joint compilation and has an issue on 3+, so is currently only applied in GROOVY_2_5_X. We are working on the joint compilation issue separately. I&apos;ll leave this open in anticipation of fixing that problem.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
